---
title: Cal Smart Creamy Sun-Dried Tomato Chicken with Garlic Veggie Jumble
description: Can you ever have enough sauce? Probably not, and this dish is all about that! Sun-dried tomato pesto and cream coat perfectly roasted chicken breasts and garlicky veggies for a truly luxurious dinner.

